Definition: conformity to reality or actuality
Example: they debated the truth of the proposition; the situation brought home to us the blunt truth of the military threat; he was famous for the truth of his portraits; he turned to religion in his search for eternal verities
Synonyms: falsity, the_true, verity, trueness, adj, all, true, actuality, conformity, to, reality, or, they, debated, the, of, proposition, situation, brought, home, us, blunt, military, threat, he, was, famous, for, his, portraits, turned, religion, in, search, eternal, verities
Category: noun.state
